thresholds.columnId: Crash count (by OS, app version) [mobile, custom]

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT startTime as [Crash Time], usersession.manufacturer as [Manufacturer], usersession.osVersion as [OS Version], usersession.appVersion as [App Version], usersession.connectionType as [Connection Type], name as Crash FROM usererror where application= "iOS Mobile Mod App (MO3607) - Prod" and type="Crash" ORDER BY startTime DESC

tiles.name: Markdown
tiles.markdown: ## **‚ùå Last 30 Days Crash Reason by App Version**

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT name as Crash, usersession.appVersion AS [App Version], COUNT(*) AS [Number of Crashes] FROM usererror where application= "iOS Mobile Mod App (MO3607) - Prod" and type="Crash" GROUP BY name, usersession.appVersion ORDER BY usersession.appVersion DESC

tiles.markdown:

tiles.name: Crash Rate by User Session (10min intervals)
User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as [Crashes], usersession.osVersion as [OS Version] FROM usererror where application= "iOS Mobile Mod App (MO3607) - Prod" and type="Crash" GROUP BY usersession.osVersion ORDER BY Crashes DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query

tiles.name: Crash Rate by User Session (Day intervals)
User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select usersession.crashGroupId as "Crash ID", useraction.name as "User Action", usersession.userActionCount as "Number of Actions", usersession.device as "Device", usersession.osVersion as "OS Version", usersession.appVersion as "App Version" FROM useraction where usersession.crashGroupId is not NULL and isExitAction=true and application="iOS Mobile Mod App (MO3607) - Prod"
